original_title: Outdoors with T.K. and Mike: Elk Huntin'
overview: The professional outdoorsmen travel to New Mexico in search of a Wapiti (North America Elk); and in the process, they bag Big Foot.
tagline: 800 pounds, big horned and meaty...Sit back and relax as we slam Wapiti
title: Outdoors with T.K. and Mike: Elk Huntin'
